	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fui his diebus una cum d. <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculo</persName>, dum ferias habemus autumnales, Neocomi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Farellus, qui se valde humanum nobis exhibuit, te et omnes fratres, qui sunt illic, plurimum salutat.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expectatur, quid <persName type="auto_name">Pagani</persName> denuo agant in causa ministri <persName type="auto_name">S. Blasii</persName>, qui praeterquam quod vicinorum voce usus est, nihil est locutus, quod quemquam vel laedere vel offendere possit.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed sine dubio latet etiam alius anguis in hac herba.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audiemus, quid venturum sit ex comitiis illis <placeName type="auto_name">Badensibus</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nostri neminem mittere voluerunt propter causas, de quibus prius scripsi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bellum contra Gallum a Caesare in <placeName type="auto_name">Burgundia</placeName> iam publice promulgatum et proclamatum est.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Maria</persName>, soror <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesaris</persName>, in <placeName type="auto_name">Picardia</placeName> molitur aliquid contra <persName type="auto_name">Gallum</persName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ipse interea sęvit in pios declarans se non cum papatu, sed cum <persName type="auto_name">Iulio</persName> bellum gerere.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Metuo valde de huic regno propter sanguinem christianum, quem fudit, et nobis quoque, qui ab illius commercio tot periculis et malis edocti nondum tamen abstinere didicimus prorsus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Unsers schultheß <persName ref="p2305" cert="high">Nägelins</persName> sünen einer ist von dem <placeName type="auto_name">Gonzaga</placeName> zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Meiland</placeName> gefangen, als er gen <placeName ref="l1122" cert="high">Parma</placeName> wellen.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Den hatt der Müßer erfaren und begert an <placeName type="auto_name">Gonzagam</placeName>, das er inn imm laße, welchs er thon.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der schlecht jetz uff ein rantzung 4m kronen, wil damitt dem vatter intrencken, was er vornaher in siner sach ghandlet; er ist angschafft.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ist aber eben deß rechten: bhieltend wir unsere kind daheim und lartinds werchen, so bschech inen das nitt.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Uns muͦß aber also deß <placeName type="auto_name">Frantzosen</placeName> werden, damitt wir nitt vergeben frantzösisch sigind.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man wirt gsen, ob er möchte gegen deß küngs gfangnen einem gelediget werden.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec habui modo.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exemplarium <persName type="auto_name">Vergerii</persName> nulla mitto propter tempestatem; literas tamen, quas simul mitto, illi dabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta uxorem, liberos, fratres; salutant vos quoque mei.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 4. calendis octobris 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[oannes] Hall[erus</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. Heinrycho Bullingero, Tigurinae ecclesiae pastori fidelissimo, domino et compatri suo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
